China to Shut Down Private Butchers to Enhance Meat Safety

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-10-09T06:24:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-09/china-to-shut-down-private-butchers-to-enhance-meat-safety.html
China  will start shutting down
private butchers nationwide this month to enhance meat safety,
the Ministry of Commerce said in a statement on its website
today. All pork sold in cities and towns should come from
designated butchers by the end of 2012, the statement said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
